welcome_message_body: Welcome to Picnic Point! Prepare to be enchanted by our charming city known for its picturesque views and outdoor activities. We invite you to explore and indulge in all that Picnic Point has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport handles all commercial flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport serves as the primary hub for all commercial and private flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free wifi throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport handles all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for cargo and general aviation.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Renton Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Renton Airport is dedicated to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport and is free for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is the largest and busiest terminal, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for domestic flights, with a focus on Alaska Airlines.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for international flights, with a focus on Delta Air Lines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout all terminals at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport.
